data.description: Welcome to this updated grand brick home in the Village of Mexico. The current owners opened it up as a single family home but it can easily be turned back into a 2 unit by closing up two doors for income potential. The large lower main unit is 2 bedroom 2 1/2 baths and the upper unit is 2 bedrooms 2 baths. The open attic is great for extra space or storage as well as an attached 2 car garage. Enjoy the charming village on the large front porches.
